casebody.data:
Leroy Miller v. The State. No. 23516. Delivered December 11, 1946.

*612The opinion states the case.

No attorney of record on appeal for appellant. Ernest S. Goens, State’s Attorney, of Austin, for the State. BEAUCHAMP, Judge.

The record before us contains no notice of appeal. Consequently, this court is without jurisdiction to consider the case.

The appeal is dismissed.
